    <subfield code="u">http://inspirehep.net/record/1250265/files/fig6.png</subfield>
    <subfield code="y">00005 Histograms resulting from the Monte Carlo analysis for 9000 parameter sets (per spectrum) for all selected spectra with $f_{\rm s}&amp;lt;25$\%. The level of confidence on the lower limits on $a_*$ are 99.7\% ($3\sigma$).</subfield>
